high_descs: walk forwards to the end of the room, then turn left to face the kitchen counter
grab the butter knife off of the counter
slice the lettuce on top of the counter
place the butter knife on the counter
grab a slice of lettuce off of the counter
turn around and walk down the hall, then turn left to stand in front of the sink
place the lettuce in the kitchen sink and rinse if off, then pick it back up
turn right and head to the end of the room, turn left to face the refrigerator
place the lettuce in the refrigerator and close the door
anns.task_desc: place a clean slice of lettuce in the refrigerator

high_descs: go forward to counter with lettuce
pick up knife from counter behind lettuce
place knife on counter in front of lettuce
slice lettuce on counter
pick up slice of lettuce from counter
turn around, go to sink
place lettuce in sink, fill sink with water, remove lettuce from sink
go to refrigerator to the right
place lettuce on middle rack of refrigerator
anns.task_desc: Place clean lettuce slice on middle rack of refrigerator

high_descs: Go forward and face the counter on your left.
Take the knife from the counter in front of you.
Slice the green fruit on the counter in front of you.
Put the knife on the counter in front of you.
Take a slice from the green fruit on the counter in front of you.
Turn around to face the sink in front of you.
Put the green fruit in the sink then open the faucet, drain the sink and take the green fruit from the sink.
Turn right and face the fridge to your left.
Open the fridge in front of you, place the green fruit inside and close the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean piece of green fruit in the fridge.
